1962;;The Playboy of the Western World;;British;;Brian Desmond Hurst;;Gary Raymond, Siobhán McKenna;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Playboy_of_the_Western_World_(film);;A young man from a far away village appears in County Mayo announcing to all and sundry that he has murdered his father with a blow to the head. With the tale growing in the telling, the young man becomes a local hero…until his angry father comes to fetch him home.